{"tid":404427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"32年前藉「檢查」非禮親女 七旬老翁囚32個月","createTime":"2017-09-18T06:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T07:20:30.000Z","uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"418eae8a9b71a633a41275a1445212bd1ef50a17","tid":404427,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">32年前藉「檢查」非禮親女 七旬老翁囚32個月</span><br />\n<br />\n44歲女兒指控父親32年前自她12歲由內地來港定居起多次性侵犯她，其中包括捉她的手摸其陽具、藉詞「檢查」而摸及舐其下體等，歷時長達7年，女兒及後終離家出走，父女不相往來逾20年。及至近年胞弟結婚與父再碰面後，女兒決定報警。父親早前經審訊後被裁定罪成，今被判入獄2年8個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告被裁定向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為及非禮共4罪。辯方今求情時指女事主創傷報告顯示她雖有受案件影響，但因有宗教信仰故情況不嚴重；被告報告則指他重犯機會非常低，辯方要求法庭考慮事主相隔多年才報案，今次事件會影響被告另一段婚姻的家庭，而案底對他亦算懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑則指女事主早年受侵犯，年青時已沒正常社交，多年後雖未致創傷後遺症但內心仍十分掙扎，考慮案情等因素，決定判被告入獄2年8個月。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57224660&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57224660%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=dBg6tSW81F0Leg6ahdWzMWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=7bb94ecc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57224660%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=58f3bf6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57224660&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"3ba923111f96d5c4d3cf4ca260ea01c69dfbb8e1","tid":404427,"uid":139139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:08:07.000Z","msg":"32年前，而家仲揾到證據入罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f375062e1a85d06cc7e2f3a40cef0fb7c5dc4003","tid":404427,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"Agentcc (七旬老翁)"},{"pid":"71a4be4080df9ca63b59571fa808f625325551a4","tid":404427,